Net,WCF,Win service,Web service,JSON,Jquery,C#, Ajax, JavaScript, Bootstrap,IIS 6.0 and SQL Server 2005 and 2008.    Project # 2 : PXD Portal  Duration : September 2013 - April 2015.  Role : Analyzing,Designing,Development and Enhancement.  Project Details :   It is an ERP for Release Order (RO) . The release order controls of the flow of Film Digital Process (FDP) which agreed with Customer and Company. The FDP provide services as advertisement, Film or Trailer. If advertisement or trailer project related working team push the logs (a log file as input data) from certain theaters (as per PXD register) to given as input. Prospectus PXD team group the log file as per RO file then generated a report and invoicing to certain clients.  Responsibilities :   Developed complex sub modules like segregate a abstract data (based on RO) from pushing log file and grouping it properly, send a mail when every time a key will be generated, Maintaining a group of log file.  Participation in creating theater confirmation listing auto mailer reports and auto log pulling (PXD registered theaters log file pulled down using V-Sat connectivity) file containing list auto mailer reports.  Role :   Involved in requirement analysis with Project Manager and identifying the components through Data Flow Diagram and generate the process based reports then involved to improve this project to enable other regions of Prasad corporation.  Environment : Asp. Net,Win service,Web service,JSON,Jquery,C#, Ajax, JavaScript, Bootstrap,IIS 6.0 and SQL Server 2005 and 2008.    Project # 3 : Prasad Portal  Duration : September 2013 - April 2015.  Role : Analyzing,Designing,Development and Enhancement.  Project Details :   It is an ERP for Sales order, Film Restoration, CG, Scanning, Recording, Audio, HD Telecine and other services. The work team enters the details for certain services for the whole day and before enter a information about	  Project and assign a project and team, then to enter the input details. Each team work based on work order from the sales team, if scanning the corresponding teams like DI, CG, RST or sales given the work order.  Role & Responsibilities :   Developed complex sub modules like Scanning and Recording (S&R) ,DI, CG, RST and Push the daily QW (Quote Works) MS-Access file to MS-SQL certain sales details table and also send the auto mailer reports based on daily utilization works in certain teams.  Participation in touch up with clients and workout for solve any issues while using a process.  Discuss with Team to improve a module and also discuss about new preparation and maintenance, for other product processors.  Involved in requirement analysis and identifying the components through Data Flow Diagram.  Involved in developing the C# Component.  Environment : Asp. Net, Asp. Net,Win service,Web service,JSON,Jquery,C#, Ajax, JavaScript, Bootstrap,IIS 6.0 and SQL Server 2005 and 2008.
